<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink89-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">talaimakaṉ talaimakaḷaip pōṟṟi oḻukāniṉṟāṉ eṉpatu kēṭṭa kātaṟparattai avaṉ pāṇaṉukkuc colluvāḷāy avaṭkup pāṅkāyiṉār kēṭpac colliyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink89">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>amma vāḻi pāṇa vevvaik</l>
<l>kevaṉperi taḷikku meṉpa paḻaṉattu</l>
<l>vaṇṭutā tūtu mūraṉ</l>
<l>peṇṭeṉa virumpiṉ ṟavaṭaṉ paṇpē.</l>
</lg>

<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


<l>   Ah, long life to you, o bard! </l> 
<l>   They ask why the man from the village </l> 
<l rend="indent2">       where bees feed on pollen at the tank</l> 
<l>   cares so much for our sister: </l> 
<l>   He wants her because of her qualities as a woman. </l> 

  
            
  
          </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
